|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]
|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社
|date=1961年
|volume=53
|title=''Quandoquidem novae''
|page=94
|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2053%20%5B1961%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|access-date=2013-11-29
|archive-date=2013-10-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007213220/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2053%20%5B1961%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。2004年有教友468,000人，佔總人口90.0%。有卅八個堂區、司鐸七十八人。現任教區主教為{{link-pt|若瑟·埃烏德斯·坎波斯·多·納斯西門托|José Eudes Campos do Nascimento}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 12.12.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/12/181212a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715173057/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/12/181212a.html |archivedate=2019-07-15 |language=en |date=2018-12-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pt|瓦爾德馬爾·查韋斯·德·阿奧霍|Waldemar Chaves de Araújo}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 26.05.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/05/26/0345/00784.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715181437/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/05/26/0345/00784.html |archivedate=2019-07-15 |language=it |date=2010-05-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

